-----------------------
Libmonitor Build Notes
-----------------------

Home: http://hpctoolkit.org

Git: https://github.com/hpctoolkit/libmonitor

git clone https://github.com/hpctoolkit/libmonitor

License: BSD

Uses Autoconf and Automake, supports vpath and parallel make.

./configure  \
    CC=compiler  \
    CFLAGS=flags  \
    --prefix=PATH  \
    --enable-client-signals='...'
make -j 4
make install

A Rice HPCToolkit project, one of ours.

Notes
1. On Blue Gene/Q backend, need to use powerpc64-bgq-linux-gcc.

